title: Kamakshi's Kitchen Vegetarian Indian Restaurant
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Pizza, Indian, Delivery, Take-out, Asian, Catering, Indo-Chinese
description: Full service restaurant featuring a daily changing menu which is posted on facebook. Specialty is North and South Indian vegetarian cuisine as well as Indo-Chinese and other international flavors. Brunch is offered on weekends til 3pm. Kitchen stops 15 minutes before closing time. Moved here from San Mateo since spring 2014.
